Package lu.uni.geko.commands

The commands package of the main plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractEcoreFilesHandler An abstract handler for commands that are only available if Ecore metamodels have been selected.
AbstractFileHandler An abstract handler for commands that discriminate selected files based on their type and create a Runnable for the selected files.
AbstractFolderHandler An abstract handler for commands that only take selected folders into account.
AbstractSingleFileTypeHandler An abstract handler for commands that discriminate only between a single file type and create a Runnable for each selected file URI.
DetectJoinpointsHandler A handler for the command that detects the joinpoints for the selected pointcut and base model.
GenerateAdviceMMHandler A handler for the command that generates an advice metamodel from the selected base metamodel and registers an editor for it.
GenerateBasePCAndAVEditorsHandler A handler for the command that generates a pointcut and an advice metamodel from the selected base metamodel and registers editors for them.
GeneratePointcutMMHandler A handler for the command that generates a pointcut metamodel from the selected base metamodel and registers an editor for it.
InstallAndStartGeneratedEditorPluginHandler A handler for the command that installs and starts the editor plugin that was created for the metamodel at the given URI.
TestWeaverHandler A handler for the command that compares the weaving result to the woven archetype in all selected folders.
WeaveInferringPc2AvMappingHandler A handler for the command that weaves the selected base, pointcut and advice models to a new woven model by inferring the mapping from pointcut to advice.

Package lu.uni.geko.commands Description

The commands package of the main plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. It contains handlers for all commands defined by this plug-in.
